Liz Hurley, 57, sparked a frenzy with the latest Instagram snaps from her idyllic trip to the Maldives. The ageless actress donned a bright blue, tie-string bikini which was adorned with silver embellishments on the top. Elizabeth was filmed frolicking in the turquoise ocean as she proudly showed off her fabulous figure. In the comments, Ryan exclaimed: "One of the hottest women alive today." While and unnamed user gushed: "Reminds me of a Bond Girl prancing in the waves."